            "title": "盤中速報 - 悅城(6405)大漲8.75%，報41.65元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>悅城(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6405:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6405\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6405-TW</a>)28日09:48股價上漲3.35元，報41.65元，漲幅8.75%，成交3,095張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>悅城(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6405:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6405\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6405-TW</a>)所屬產業為光電業，主要業務為光電薄化玻璃。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.22%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲7.19%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+36 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+27 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+9 張</li> <li>融資增減：+155 張</li> <li>融券增減：-1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
